<paragraph blockId="31.[151,1436,1477,1682]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
Listed from East Azarbaijan by 
<bibRefCitation author="Khaghaninia" box="[519,819,1513,1538]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" refString="Khaghaninia, S., Farshbaf Pour-Abad, R. &amp; Askari, O. (2010 b) First record for seven species of leaf bugs (Hemiptera, Miridae) for Iran insect fauna from East Azarbayjan province. Munis Entomology &amp; Zoology, 5 (1), 309 - 310." type="journal article" year="2010" yearSuffix="b">
Khaghaninia 
<emphasis box="[671,722,1513,1538]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">et al</emphasis>
. (
<number box="[745,805,1513,1538]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" value="2010.0">2010</number>
b
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Khaghaninia" box="[833,893,1514,1538]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" refString="Khaghaninia, S., Farshbaf Pour-Abad, R. &amp; Askari, O. (2011) A contribution to the Heteroptera fauna of Zunuz region, northwest of Iran. North-Western Journal of Zoology, 7 (1), 35 - 38." type="journal article" year="2011">
<number box="[833,893,1514,1538]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" value="2011.0">2011</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). Its presence in 
<collectingCountry box="[1087,1132,1514,1537]" name="Iran" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">Iran</collectingCountry>
on peppermint and alfalfa (
<bibRefCitation author="Khaghaninia" box="[158,453,1549,1574]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" refString="Khaghaninia, S., Farshbaf Pour-Abad, R. &amp; Askari, O. (2011) A contribution to the Heteroptera fauna of Zunuz region, northwest of Iran. North-Western Journal of Zoology, 7 (1), 35 - 38." type="journal article" year="2011">
Khaghaninia 
<emphasis box="[318,381,1549,1574]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">et al.</emphasis>
<number box="[396,453,1550,1574]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" value="2011.0">2011</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) should be verified by an analysis of the East Azarbaijan specimens studied by Khaghaninia 
<emphasis box="[301,357,1585,1610]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">et al.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[373,401,1586,1609]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">op</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[415,443,1586,1609]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">cit</emphasis>
.) (
<bibRefCitation author="Aukema" box="[474,702,1585,1610]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" refString="Aukema, B., Rieger, C. &amp; Rabitsch, W. (2013) Catalogue of the Heteroptera of the Palaearctic Region. Vol. 6. Supplement. Netherlands Entomological Society. Ponsen &amp; Looijen, Wageningen, 628 pp." type="book" year="2013">
Aukema 
<emphasis box="[578,634,1585,1610]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">et al.</emphasis>
<number box="[641,702,1586,1610]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" value="2013.0">2013</number>
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="31.[151,1436,1477,1682]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,404,1621,1646]" pageId="31" pageNumber="32">General distribution.</emphasis>
